## 6. TRANSLATE() vs REPLACE()

**TRANSLATE:** character by character replacement
**REPLACE:** string by string replacement

```sql
select translate('india','in','xy'), replace('india','in','xy') from dual;
```

Output → xydia | xdyia

```sql
select translate('JOHN','H','N') from dual;
```

Output → JONN

